Livingston, wishing the best to all of our readers and friends in Los Angel=
es dealing with the horrific wildfires in the city. Peter Hamby will have a=
n update on the situation there on tomorrow=E2=80=99s episode of The Powers=
 That Be.

=C2=A0

In tonight=E2=80=99s edition, we lead with my partner Dylan Byers=E2=80=99s=
 sharp reporting on the the fears engulfing
several germane fixtures of the Fourth Estate=E2=80=94The Washington Post, =
