=E2=80=8A

The Hill Braces for Trump 2.0
-----------------------------

Congress is in session and busy with floor speeches, nominee meetings, and =
news
conferences galore. But everyone knows that even though it feels like Donal=
d Trump is already president again, we=E2=80=99re still in the pseudo-inter=
